00:01:16.805 --> 00:01:18.485
such as the event names,

00:01:18.485 --> 00:01:21.110
the details, all the background colors.

00:01:21.110 --> 00:01:23.945
But one thing to note is these dates.

00:01:23.945 --> 00:01:28.775
Very soon, we're going to need some event date which in the past or have expired.

00:01:28.775 --> 00:01:30.980
