00:01:43.910 --> 00:01:48.920
We'll need to go over to the terminal and also install this too.

00:01:48.920 --> 00:01:52.970
If you use any built-in at terminal inside a Visual Studio code,

00:01:52.970 --> 00:01:55.550
you'd go to Terminal, New Terminal,

00:01:55.550 --> 00:01:58.840
and this would be opened up inside of your project folder.

00:01:58.840 --> 00:02:00.770
If you use any separate terminal,

00:02:00.770 --> 00:02:02.915
you will need to use the CD command,

00:02:02.915 --> 00:02:06.275
which is going to navigate to our project directory.

00:02:06.275 --> 00:02:08.845
Mine is saved on the desktop.

00:02:08.845 --> 00:02:12.650
To begin it, let's CD into the repository folder,

00:02:12.650 --> 00:02:15.665
which is the vue-3-course-master.

00:02:15.665 --> 00:02:20.710
Then from here, you will CD into the view Countdown Starter.

00:02:20.710 --> 00:02:23.700
Make sure you are in the correct folder.

00:02:23.700 --> 00:02:31.155
Then we're going to install the node modules with npm i. Npm i is short for installed.

00:02:31.155 --> 00:02:35.550
This will pull in all of the packages which we need for this project.

00:02:47.060 --> 00:02:54.220
Once this is done, we can start up the development server with npm run serve.

00:02:58.310 --> 00:03:02.540
then this is going to open up our project on local-host.

00:03:02.540 --> 00:03:04.760
If we Command or Control click,

00:03:04.760 --> 00:03:07.690
this will open this up inside of the browser.

00:03:07.690 --> 00:03:09.390
While developing this project.

00:03:09.390 --> 00:03:11.930
We can leave this development server running.

00:03:11.930 --> 00:03:13.790
But if we want to close this down,

00:03:13.790 --> 00:03:16.790
all we need to do is to press Control-C,

00:03:16.790 --> 00:03:21.335
which will close down our development server so we can no longer access our site.

00:03:21.335 --> 00:03:23.090
Then to restart things,

00:03:23.090 --> 00:03:26.815
we then run npm run serve once again.

00:03:26.815 --> 00:03:31.590
We can now access our project once again in the browser.
